    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "the goblin thing was a bit of a weird comparison lol. but anyway, you mentioned the interest is calculated on the balance remaining after the previous payment. does that mean there are specific days in the month where the interest accrues faster, or is it just a flat rate applied to the whole month? i just want to make sure i understand the exact timing of how these costs get tacked on.",
